  "content": "The third principle of Open-Source Capitalism is reinvestment through Revenue-Generating Hubs (RGHs). Monetized OSS must funnel returns back to the contributors. The RGH manages licensing, sales, and commercial transactions in alignment with decentralized values, supporting revenue streams including enterprise licensing, SaaS subscriptions, and consulting services.",
